title: Inside Gaza: a life under blockade
text:
Inside Gaza: a life under blockade Wednesday, May 16, 2018 - 02:33
As protests lessen on the Israel-Gaza border where dozens of Palestinians were killed by Israeli gunfire this week, Reuters Emily Wither speaks to some of the two million people facing blockade and crippling unemployment in the narrow strip.
